      "text": "LizNoirライブツアー、北海道公演\n僕達も最高に楽しい時間だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "LizNoir Live Tour‚ Hokkaido Performance\nIt was the best time for us too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.8419987239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_circularstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 12.1490021388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "生こころのパフォーマンス\nもちろん目に焼き付けてくれましたよねー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro's live performance\nOf course you burned it into your eyes‚ right~!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4156688054,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_circularstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 18.1156688054
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "私達はもちろん、スペシャルゲストのミクちゃんにも\nご声援感謝でーす！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To us‚ and of course to our special guest Miku too\nThank you for your support~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.0823354721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_circularstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 24.7490021388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-ymk002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう！　私も、すっごく楽しかったよ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you! I had so much fun too!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7490021388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_circularstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 29.8709534327
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "名残惜しいけど、いよいよ本当に終わりの時間です……\n本日はご来場――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's sad to say goodbye‚ but it's finally time to end…\nThank you for coming today——",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.6156623321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_circularstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 36.6395020485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとうございました！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.6395020485,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 430.74910029999813,
