        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.0739685058
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.0739685058
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、お疲れ様\n最高のライブになったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good job‚ everyone\nIt was the best live performance",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2073018391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.2260805529
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "当然じゃないですか～\nこころが立つステージに、最高以外はあり得ませんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Isn't that obvious~\nA stage where I stand can't be anything less than the best",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3739685058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "こころってば……\nでも、盛り上がってくれたみたいでホッとしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro…\nBut I'm relieved that the audience seemed excited",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.5927456935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.5927472195
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "何、他人事みたいに言ってるのさ。当事者なのに\n僕達全員の努力の成果だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why are you talking like it's someone else's business? You're part of this too\nIt's the result of all our efforts",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6406351725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.91828026
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "そうよ\n今日のライブはお世辞抜きに、誇っていい出来だった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right\nToday's live was‚ without flattery‚ something to be proud of",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.4109546899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "ミクも、お疲れ様\n出演してくれて本当にありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku‚ good job\nThank you so much for performing with us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9442880232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.6632236562
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ymk",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ymk.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-ymk003.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそ、ありがとう！\nライブってやっぱり楽しいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you too!\nLives are really fun‚ aren't they",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7073018391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.8298903229
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、そうね\n新曲も、みんな盛り上がってくれていたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ that's right\nEveryone got excited about the new song too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9776213566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "アイデアが出るまでは、毎度のごとく\nこころに振り回されて頭を抱えたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Until we came up with the idea‚ as always\nI was driven crazy by Kokoro…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3109546899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.5124753399
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "え～、そういう莉央さんだって\n全然いい案出してなかったじゃないですか～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well~‚ even you Rio\nYou didn't come up with any good ideas either~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.1458071472,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.4124753399
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "否定は出来ないわね……悔しいけれど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't deny it… unfortunately…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4124753399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.7665568593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "でもそうやってみんなでアイデアを出し合ったおかげで\n最高の一曲を届けられたのかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But thanks to everyone contributing ideas like that\nWe might have been able to deliver the best song",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7442880232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.8637678705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "同感です！\nけど、うまくまとめてごまかそうとしてませんか～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I agree!\nBut aren't you trying to gloss over it~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2970996779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.2637678705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……ともあれ、ここで立ち話もなんだ\n楽屋に戻って、一息つこうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha… anyway‚ standing here and talking is a bit\nWhy don't we go back to the dressing room and take a break?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7442880232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.3193007393
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.3193007393
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "着替えまで済ませると、途端に\nライブ終わったんだなって名残惜しくなるわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once we change clothes‚ suddenly\nI feel sad that the live is over",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7442880232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.3468733411
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "北海道にいられるのもあと二日\nあっという間だったわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We only have two more days in Hokkaido\nIt went by so quickly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.4776213566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
