      "text": "ライブの準備と、合間にローカル局の番組出演\n加えて新曲のレッスンも、急遽差し込みましたからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Between live preparations and local TV show appearances\nPlus‚ we urgently added lessons for the new song",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.5442880232,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "けど、完璧にやり遂げたのはさすがですよ\n今回のことは、他のグループの刺激にもなるはずです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But pulling it off perfectly is really amazing\nThis will definitely inspire other groups too",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.6739685058,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
