      "text": "ミクとの共演を果たせたのは間違いなく\n貴方の尽力のおかげだもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Undoubtedly‚ it was\nThanks to your efforts",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.8109546899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
