      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ymk_01_01-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "新曲の準備にも協力してもらったことだし\n改めてお礼がしたいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She also cooperated with us on the new song preparation\nI'd like to thank her again",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.2776213566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
